"{\"uid\": \"oann.com-newsroom-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-rehearsal-postponed-due-to-seine-river-pollution\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"OAN'sAbril Elfi3:40 PM - Saturday, June 22, 2024  A monitoring report from the city of Paris has revealed that the Seine river remains too dirty to accommodate the Paris Olympics triathlon and open-water swimming events.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 87, \"end\": 92, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999994526714678, \"rank\": 5.473287772172827e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 115, \"end\": 120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999931438263434, \"rank\": 6.780230111768486e-06, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to the report, routine samples taken from June 10thto June 16that various locations along the Seine revealed elevated levels of E. coli bacteria.\", \"from\": 222, \"to\": 377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 326, \"end\": 331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999931438263434, \"rank\": 6.780230111768486e-06, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris organizes triathlon and marathon swimming competitions for athletes to take place in the Seine during the Olympics.\", \"from\": 379, \"to\": 500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 379, \"end\": 384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999994526714678, \"rank\": 5.473287772172827e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 474, \"end\": 479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999931438263434, \"rank\": 6.780230111768486e-06, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According toThe Associated Press, the men's triathlon is the first such event and is set for July 30th.\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 604, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 517, \"end\": 533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999666051081583, \"rank\": 3.339596455870538e-05, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The city of Paris spent roughly $1.5 billion cleaning up its outdated sewage system, which overflows into the river during periods of intense precipitation.\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 762, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 618, \"end\": 623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999994526714678, \"rank\": 5.473287772172827e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest report stated that the water quality was considerably reduced due to the unusually high rainfall in May and the recent wet days.\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 903, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It also mentioned the absence of sunny days or times with reduced streamflow, which can aid in the reduction of bacteria.\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 1026, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The sun does inactivate the bacteria,\\\" said Helena Solo-Gabriele, a professor in the University of Miami's department of chemical, environmental, and materials engineering.\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1201, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1073, \"end\": 1079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_Helena\", \"score\": 0.9927581882521705, \"rank\": 0.007278505940267451, \"text\": \"Helena\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_Helena\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_Helena\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, Solo-Gabriele noted that unsafe fecal matter levels in swimming pools could result in gastrointestinal disorders.\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1330, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Although they have not done so yet, French President Emmanuel Macron and Paris Mayor Anne Hidalgo have promised to swim in the Seine to demonstrate its cleanliness.\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1496, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1368, \"end\": 1384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\"}, {\"begin\": 1385, \"end\": 1400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 1405, \"end\": 1416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Mayor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1417, \"end\": 1429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anne Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\"}, {\"begin\": 1459, \"end\": 1464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999931438263434, \"rank\": 6.780230111768486e-06, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay informed!\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1512, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Receive breaking news blasts directly to your inbox for free.\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1574, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe here.https://www.oann.com/alerts    What do YOU think?\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1639, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Click here to jump to the comments!\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1675, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share this post!\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1695, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Accessibility Tools\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1722, \"entities\": []}]}"